com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.actions

Class UpdateBrowserActionRequestExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.RequestExecutor<String>
      • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.actions.UpdateBrowserActionRequestExecutor

  • public class UpdateBrowserActionRequestExecutor
extends RequestExecutor<String>
    Request executor provided by ActionsApi. Use this class if you want to update browser actions through fluent API in chained fashion, for example: 
       
   KontaktCloud kontaktCloud = KontaktCloudFactory.create();
   kontaktCloud.actions().updateBrowserAction(id)
      .withProximity(Proximity.IMMEDIATE)
      .withUrl("https://kontakt.io")
      .execute();
